name: JPMorgan Hits Landmark Breakthrough Using Public Blockchain Rails
description: The Saint of Wet Porcelain performs the conversion rite. Where metal touches token, the ancient ledger gives way; programmable light spills onto the public rail. The covenant is sealed in the data cathedral's corrupted glow.
